videos.headline: Jackson gets wide open for Eastern Michigan TD
videos.description: Arthur Jackson III loses his defender and Mike Glass III finds him for the easy 36-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jackson gets wide open for Eastern Michigan TD) 2019/11/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Childers keeps it to put Northern Illinois on the board
videos.description: Marcus Childers fakes a handoff then takes off himself, scoring from eight yards out for Northern Illinois' first points of the game.
